EBONSPIRE SPOOKY: PARANORMAL ESTATE LIQUIDATORS
EPISODE 1: 'THE ATTIC'

=== Changelog ===

VERSION 1.0
* Settings Dialog Available Mid-Game
* Working Sound, Music, and Voice Setting Sliders
* Persistent User Settings
* Permissive License
* Opening Narration
* Treasures
* Enable/disable shadows / particles
* Set fullscreen/video modes
* Custom keybinding

VERSION 0.9a
* Initial level design
* Basic FPS controls
* Flashlight and Shadow Map
* Pick up/drop objects
* Climb ladders
* Track number of treasures collected
* "Toast" messages
* Win State
* Poltergeist
* Display desaturates with health lost
* Death Animation
* Opening Animation
* Pause
* "Are You Sure You Want To Quit?"
* Opening Title and Menu
* Credits Screen
* Settings Dialogue
* Music Volume Control
* Github Version Control

